*{{SCP|Defence|85+|link=yes}}
*{{SCP|Ranged|75+|link=yes}}
*{{SCP|Prayer|70+|link=yes}} ([[Piety]], 74+ [[Rigour]])
*{{SCP|Magic|76|link=yes}} and completion of [[A Kingdom Divided]] (if using [[thrall]]s, 80 for [[Death Charge]])

